{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":817,"text":"I was six when I had the first chance\nto learn what patience means."},{"time":6099,"text":"My grandmother gave me a magic box\nas a birthday present,"},{"time":9485,"text":"which neither of us knew\nwould become a gift for life."},{"time":13817,"text":"I became obsessed with magic,"},{"time":16318,"text":"and at 20, I became\nan amateur dove magician."},{"time":21467,"text":"This act of magic\nrequires that I train my doves"},{"time":24618,"text":"to sit and wait inside my clothing."},{"time":27738,"text":"As a young magician, I was always\nin a rush to make them appear,"},{"time":32485,"text":"but my teacher told me"},{"time":34056,"text":"the secret to the success\nof this magical act"},{"time":37468,"text":"is to make my doves appear\nonly after they've waited patiently"},{"time":41715,"text":"in my tuxedo."},{"time":43797,"text":"It has to be a mindful kind of patience,"},{"time":46841,"text":"the kind that took me\nsome years to master."}]},{"cues":[{"time":51789,"text":"When life took me to Shanghai\nseven years ago,"},{"time":54928,"text":"the mindful patience I learned\nbecame almost impossible to practice."},{"time":60419,"text":"In China, where everyone\nand everything is in a hurry,"},{"time":64412,"text":"you need to outperform\nover 1.3 billion other people"},{"time":67888,"text":"to build a better life."},{"time":70601,"text":"You hack the system, bend the rules,"},{"time":73039,"text":"circumvent the boundaries."},{"time":75530,"text":"It is the same when it comes to food ..."},{"time":78500,"text":"except that when it comes to food,"},{"time":81538,"text":"impatience can have dire consequences."},{"time":85618,"text":"In the haste to grow more, sell more,"},{"time":88381,"text":"4,000 years of agriculture\nin a country of rich natural resources"},{"time":93388,"text":"is spoiled by the overuse\nof chemicals and pesticides."},{"time":97650,"text":"In 2016, the Chinese government revealed"},{"time":100627,"text":"half a million food safety violations\nin just nine months."},{"time":106125,"text":"Alarmingly, one in every four\ndiabetics in the world"},{"time":109880,"text":"now comes from China."},{"time":112742,"text":"The stories around food"},{"time":114479,"text":"are scary and somewhat overwhelming,"},{"time":117965,"text":"and I told myself it's time to bring\na mindful patience into the impatience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":124352,"text":"When I say mindful patience,"},{"time":126194,"text":"I don't mean the ability to wait."},{"time":128966,"text":"I mean knowing how to act while waiting."},{"time":133751,"text":"And so, while I wait for the day"},{"time":136360,"text":"when a sustainable food system\nbecomes a reality in China,"},{"time":140352,"text":"I launched one of China's first\nonline farmers market"},{"time":143686,"text":"to bring local, organically grown\nproduce to families."},{"time":148488,"text":"When we went live, 18 months ago,"},{"time":150685,"text":"the food we could sell then\nwas somewhat dismal."},{"time":154006,"text":"We had no fruit\nand hardly any meat to sell,"},{"time":157070,"text":"as none that was sent to the lab\npassed our zero tolerance test"},{"time":161086,"text":"towards pesticides, chemicals,\nantibiotics and hormones."},{"time":165572,"text":"I told our very anxious employees"},{"time":167692,"text":"that we would not give up until we've met\nevery local farmer in China."}]},{"cues":[{"time":173882,"text":"Today, we supply 240 types of produce"},{"time":177748,"text":"from 57 local farmers."},{"time":180732,"text":"After almost one year of searching,"},{"time":183330,"text":"we finally found chemical-free bananas"},{"time":186201,"text":"grown in the backyards\nof villagers on Hainan Island."},{"time":190569,"text":"And only two hours away from Shanghai,"},{"time":193376,"text":"on an island that even Google Maps\ndoes not have coordinates for,"},{"time":197471,"text":"we found a place where cows eat grass"},{"time":200265,"text":"and roam free under the blue sky."},{"time":203941,"text":"We also work hard on logistics."},{"time":206690,"text":"We deliver our customers' orders\nin as fast as three hours"},{"time":210135,"text":"on electric vehicles,"},{"time":212103,"text":"and we use biodegradable, reusable boxes"},{"time":214826,"text":"to minimize our environmental footprint."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218885,"text":"I have no doubt that our offerings\nwill continue to grow,"},{"time":222941,"text":"but it will take time,"},{"time":224878,"text":"and I know a lot more people are needed\nto shape the future of good food."},{"time":230390,"text":"So last year, I founded China's first\nfood tech accelerator and VC platform"},{"time":235883,"text":"to help start-ups to shape\nthe future of good food"},{"time":238868,"text":"the way they want,"},{"time":240455,"text":"be that through using edible insects\nas a more sustainable source of protein"},{"time":245424,"text":"or using essential oils\nto keep food fresh for longer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":250514,"text":"So, you may still ask:"},{"time":252618,"text":"Why are you trying to build\na sustainable food system"},{"time":255959,"text":"by driving a patient movement"},{"time":257966,"text":"in a country where it's almost\na crime to take it slow?"},{"time":262329,"text":"Because, for me,"},{"time":263710,"text":"the real secret to success is patience --"},{"time":267290,"text":"a mindful kind of patience"},{"time":269123,"text":"that requires knowing\nhow to act while waiting,"},{"time":272949,"text":"the kind of patience I learned\nwith my grandmother's magic box."},{"time":277865,"text":"After all, we do not inherit\nthe earth from our ancestors."},{"time":283030,"text":"We borrow it from our children."}]},{"cues":[{"time":285199,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":286374,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}